title: Summoner level not updated, not letting me post
body:
Trying to see if what happened to this person works for me and it automagically fixes....
http://boards.na.leagueoflegends.com/en/c/site-feedback/6QJKQ2df-user-level-not-updated-on-the-boards-and-im-unable-to-reply-fixed

replies.body: It looks like your profile updated by posting here!  If you are still getting a level error in other regions of the board, you may need to [clean your cache and cookies ](https://support.riotgames.com/hc/en-us/articles/201752694-Clearing-Browser-History-and-Cookies)to update on your side locally.  A quick re-log might also help before doing that!  Hope that helps!

Or not....
It now says im lv 25, but I still cant post anywhere other than here. Already tried relogging before someone suggests that.
Oh look, it did :/ this can be closed I guess
